      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "(1:1000; Santa Cruz Biotech, Santa Cruz, CA, USA); a mAb against NHE1, clone 4F9 (1:1000; Santa Cruz Biotech); polyclonal antibodies against ACE (1:1000), a polyclonal antibody against ACE2 (1:1000; ab75762, Abcam, Cambridge, MA, USA); and a polyclonal antibody against GAPDH (1:5000; ab59351, Abcam)."
